data.text:
The Twin Cities Premier Home Builder & Remodeler

Summit Design-Build brings a dedication to excellence that goes unmatched in today’s contracting world. Summit is committed to making the building & remodeling experience enjoyable as well as delivering the highest quality custom home you deserve.​

From start to finish, Summit Design Build combines uncompromising craftsmanship with attention to detail in order to provide complete customer satisfaction. Spacious interiors, sumptuous master retreats, exquisite details, distinctive elevations, and professional workmanship from the inside out are only the beginning of the Summit commitment to excellence.

FRESH INSPIRED KITCHEN DESIGNS

CUSTOM DESIGNS TO FIT YOUR NEEDS

SUMPTUOUS MASTER BEDROOM RETREATS

​The Summit Design-Build team brings to the table an unwavering dedication to create a home that is wonderful for entertaining as it is for relaxing from life’s stresses. Summit’s commitment to excellence has resulted in some of the finest homes & remodels in the Twin Cities & Western Wisconsin homes reflecting quality and distinction as your dream home becomes a reality. Summit Design Build from Dream Home to Reality!
